&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid Search Specialist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Paid Search Specialist is a role primarily responsible for monitoring, managing, reporting, and supporting planning for paid search programs. This position should have an understanding of the program strategy and objectives to ensure a flawless execution and reporting approach that aligns with campaign goals and objectives. This position accurately executes programs while closely monitoring campaigns and delivering reporting that aligns with and accomplishes our client’s goals and objectives. Ad Operations is not a part of this role, and candidates with only AdOps experience (even if it included Search) do not meet our criteria. The position requires working during U.S. East Coast (Eastern Time) business hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
