&lt;p&gt;● Experience in running campaigns for highly regulated industry&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;● Strong understanding of Search Engine Marketing mechanisms and optimization techniques&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;● Experience with the US market&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;● Fluent English – written and oral&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;● Understanding of metrics and analytical thinking&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;● Strong attention to details&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;● Working knowledge of Google Ads, Google Analytics, and Microsoft Office Excel&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
